                </div>
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight"
                >
                    BC PNP <span class="text-green-600">2026 Allocation</span>
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
                >
                    British Columbia has received 5,254 nominations for 2026.
                    Here's everything you need to know about the new allocation
                    and what it means for applicants.
                </p>
            </header>

            <!-- Key Stats -->
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center"
